::Rust::

"I am Major Rust, soldier, and that is all that should matter to yo-" Rust 
was answering Whistler's question as he hears the bot's report about a twig 
snapping.

"SPREAD OUT!" he bellows, his gun suddenly ready, "SEARCH THE AREA!"
